title: Sidewall, ca. 1895–1914
provenance: From Voigt House, 115 College Ave., S.E., Grand Rapids, MI.
description: Medallion stripe design. Wide stripe with round medallion containing architectural fragment. This alternates vertically with foliate wreath containing women's hat. Next is a narrower band simulating moire. Entire surface is printed with a mica pigment in an off-white color.

tombstone.epitaph:
Sidewall, ca. 1895–1914.
ca. 1895–1914. Embossed paper. Gift of Samuel J. Dornsife. 1973-69-1.
